    "prompt": "<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows the sideview of a horizontal meterstick that has a uniformly distributed mass of 0.5 kilogram. The meterstick is supported by a pivot that is located 0.25 meter from its left end. Two objects, labeled A and B, are placed on the meterstick as follows. Object A has a mass of 1.0 kilogram and is placed at the left end of the meterstick. Object B has a mass of 0.5 kilogram and is placed 0.25 meter to the right of the pivot.\" height=\"137\" src=\"/images/0c9acbf71e88dffbd3d2df7ebecc3374.png\" width=\"290\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A meterstick with a uniformly distributed mass of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"0.5 kilogram\"><math alttext=\"0.5 kilogram\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>0.5 kg</mtext></math></span></span> is supported by a pivot placed at the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"0.25 meter\"><math alttext=\"0.25 meter\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>0.25 m</mtext></math></span></span> mark from the left, as shown. At the left end, a small object of mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1.0 kilogram\"><math alttext=\"1.0 kilogram\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>1.0 kg</mtext></math></span></span> is placed at the zero mark, and a second small object of mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"0.5 kilogram\"><math alttext=\"0.5 kilogram\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>0.5 kg</mtext></math></span></span> is placed at the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"0.5 meter\"><math alttext=\"0.5 meter\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>0.5 m</mtext></math></span></span> mark. The meterstick is supported so that it remains horizontal, and then it is released from rest. One second after it is released, what is the change in the angular momentum of the meterstick?</p>\n",
